{"tid":355363,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一碗正既麻辣小麵，真係唔容易","createTime":"2017-08-11T08:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T19:31:37.000Z","uid":28301,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf53d98ce69fce811c7d3ce957703c3c99307b9","tid":355363,"uid":28301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"如果大家鐘意食麻辣<br />\n請大家一定要去荃灣沙咀道球場隔離果間<br />\n<br />\n我唔係打手，無錢收<br />\n但佢地既牛筋金菇兩餸麻辣小麵（我食小辣），真係正撚到仆街<br />\n牛筋係新鮮牛筋，有香味<br />\n每次去下午都見佢地自己tur新鮮蒜蓉，辣椒<br />\n但次次去都無乜人<br />\n我好怕佢做唔住會執笠<br />\n咁我就以後都無得食咁好食咁出色既麻辣小麵<br />\n<br />\n我曾經四出找代替品，試勻哂<br />\n無一間做得好似咁好食, not even close<br />\n所以我懇請大家行過幫襯下<br />\n咪撚再食埋x仔果種水滾米線，全化學湯底，又加奶又剩，不撚知所謂，無除無味<br />\n大家要向劣食say no，幫下良心好食既小店先<br />\n<br />\nBtw 星期一唔好去，試過摸門釘，佢例休"},{"pid":"89714d564235dabf97e4ef82fdfec3a39a3d8400","tid":355363,"uid":106307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"知啦食神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1e90db3baeb119d03d72b4ba875b8caca88c56","tid":355363,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"樓豬 你條線收唔收<br />\n我收10蚊一個po<br />\n拆返2蚊比你，ok?"},{"pid":"85fcade000cb283c823be29f04fb32faa7f37457","tid":355363,"uid":48830,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"圖都無張"},{"pid":"337c5b9b4811000655090fdccf1967da821f688c","tid":355363,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"幾錢一個po?"},{"pid":"801a0432b2a029f21d7cf0dea36d64eae3e0f060","tid":355363,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢一個po?</blockquote><br />\n10蚊"},{"pid":"e6d9801caf6035577a09d53beb4a2694d5f3c750","tid":355363,"uid":28301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬 你條線收唔收<br />\n我收10蚊一個po<br />\n拆返2蚊比你，ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真講，你d野好食但又無知我怕你執我先會出post<br />\n要搵錢我大把其它方式啦，使撚喺度乞你地去幫襯咩"},{"pid":"4a11b1fcc6123f5204ab44b3abe00814b048c9c1","tid":355363,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:30:43.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫小面？<br />\n利申喺重慶"},{"pid":"a1e6fb568a485eb4a677ef9f21a34aa4da98be34","tid":355363,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T19:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知唔知咩叫小面？<br />\n利申喺重慶</blockquote><br />\nbtw有冇舖名 想試下正唔正宗"}]}